    <div class="partbox no_padding">
        <div class="partbox_item">
            <div class="part_list clearfix"><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/g2702/guide-0-0/"><img width="240" height="285" src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/Cii-T1e1b82IKjAyAAsP2gfgC54AABX4gK58kUACw_y022_w800_h0_c0_t0.jpg" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G2/M00/40/F0/Cii-T1e1b82IKjAyAAsP2gfgC54AABX4gK58kUACw_y022_w800_h0_c0_t0.jpg" style="display: inline;"></a><span class="top"><i></i>1</span></div><div class="des"><div class="note_title"><i></i><em><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/g2702/guide-0-0/" target="_blank">西安</a></em><span class="left_yh"></span><span>左手历史右手美食</span><span class="right_yh"></span></div><p class="mainmes mb_15">西安，古称长安，是陕西省省会。西安历史悠久，有着7000多年文明史、3100多年建城史、1100多年的建都史，是中华文明和中华民族重要发祥地，丝绸之路的起点。西安的文化遗存具有资源密度大、保存好、级别高的特点，是中国最佳旅游目的地城市之一。</p><div class="about_line"><ul class="clearfix"><li><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10020272"><img src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/ea8f4b9e74b753564d5c233ea791c12f_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpg" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/ea/8f/ea8f4b9e74b753564d5c233ea791c12f_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpg" style="display: inline;"></a></div><div class="des"><p class="note_title"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10020272" title="梦回长安.长安梦（5天4夜暴走西安）">梦回长安.长安梦（5天4夜暴走西安）</a></p><p class="auther"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/person/9CC98E044397300FBE9543E63A6AD021" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">来自：lanmuyoyo</a></p></div></li><li><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10002335"><img src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/91a0254c3d6917aff27e0f3d43a34691_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpg" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/91/a0/91a0254c3d6917aff27e0f3d43a34691_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpg" style="display: inline;"></a></div><div class="des"><p class="note_title"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10002335" title="【陕西】3日穷游西安，再次品味历史。">【陕西】3日穷游西安，再次品味历史。</a></p><p class="auther"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/person/31543E3D5278735132C07715B9816540" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">来自：大河</a></p></div></li><li><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/1381021"><img src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/f895dada22dd43a3884193e13eacb081_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpeg" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/f8/95/f895dada22dd43a3884193e13eacb081_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpeg" style="display: inline;"></a></div><div class="des"><p class="note_title"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/1381021" title="｜蘇朵?｜【西安】第一次差旅">｜蘇朵?｜【西安】第一次差旅</a></p><p class="auther"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/person/A0743A1D395061A705B0178918236C45" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">来自：苏朵朵</a></p></div></li><li><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/1380224"><img src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/34161d69edf246d856be650fff0f4457_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpeg" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/34/16/34161d69edf246d856be650fff0f4457_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpeg" style="display: inline;"></a></div><div class="des"><p class="note_title"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/1380224" title="为什么要一个人旅行？（洛阳，西安）">为什么要一个人旅行？（洛阳，西安）</a></p><p class="auther"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/person/F6960554FD82483F2663DB9C80600656" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">来自：旅行小熊</a></p></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="part_list clearfix"><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/g47164/guide-0-0/"><img width="240" height="285" src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/Cii9EFbL-AiIDVFPAAVvJcbABDEAACMNwOCQ-MABW89638_w800_h0_c0_t0.jpg" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/fb2/t1/G1/M00/05/A1/Cii9EFbL-AiIDVFPAAVvJcbABDEAACMNwOCQ-MABW89638_w800_h0_c0_t0.jpg" style="display: inline;"></a><span class="top"><i></i>2</span></div><div class="des"><div class="note_title"><i></i><em><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/g47164/guide-0-0/" target="_blank">京都</a></em><span class="left_yh"></span><span>最“和”不过古京都</span><span class="right_yh"></span></div><p class="mainmes mb_15">京都是一个位在日本西部近畿地方京都府南部的城市，为京都府府厅所在地。京都有众多的文化遗产，17处古迹。京都的春季开始于三月中旬，这一时期樱花盛开，吸引无数游客前往赏樱。以悠久的历史和独特的文化培育起来的京都一年中还会举行众多的庙会活动，保存了大量的文化传统。</p><div class="about_line"><ul class="clearfix"><li><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10034902"><img src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/b62a34573e99837849892c9835edc942_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpeg" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/b6/2a/b62a34573e99837849892c9835edc942_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpeg" style="display: inline;"></a></div><div class="des"><p class="note_title"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10034902" title="爱拉的京都、大阪全纪录">爱拉的京都、大阪全纪录</a></p><p class="auther"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/person/7370212AB6E53199D28B6EAB4997FBAE" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">来自：Aila爱拉</a></p></div></li><li><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10033043"><img src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/70668e01d4bb1e2561d4601a791e3b4a_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpeg" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/70/66/70668e01d4bb1e2561d4601a791e3b4a_w240_h135_c1_t0.jpeg" style="display: inline;"></a></div><div class="des"><p class="note_title"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10033043" title="【天晴姐步履不停之】东京向左，大阪往右">【天晴姐步履不停之】东京向左，大阪往右</a></p><p class="auther"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/person/810CD3DFD1676219ACFFF49D35814FCE" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">来自：天晴姐</a></p></div></li><li><div class="pic"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10021271"><img src="./攻略去哪里旅游好_去哪旅游好玩又便宜_旅游景点推荐_途牛旅游网_files/4932795ff46f031a5b7b97c54e3017fc_w240_h135_c1_t0.png" data-src="http://m.tuniucdn.com/filebroker/cdn/snc/49/32/4932795ff46f031a5b7b97c54e3017fc_w240_h135_c1_t0.png" style="display: inline;"></a></div><div class="des"><p class="note_title"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.tuniu.com/trips/10021271" title="【日本】爱在樱花漫天纷飞时，日本深度八日游（途牛销量冠军线）">【日本】爱在樱花漫天纷飞时，日本深度八日游（途牛销量冠军线）</a></p><p class="auther"><a href="http://www.tuniu.com/person/F1923D4053C117BCC1EC42B982A16354" target="_blank" rel=